  "campaign": {
    "name": "Strava | Running, Cycling & Hiking App - Train, Track & Share",
    "campaignDescription": "<p>Strava is a leading mobile app and website connecting millions of runners, cyclists, hikers, and walkers through their shared love for sports, offering tools to train, track, and share activities. Complementing this, the Global Cycling Network (GCN) highlights 9 essential, often overlooked Strava features, including AI-powered training and dark mode. Discover these hidden gems and lesser-known tricks to elevate your Strava experience, connecting with a global community and optimizing your athletic pursuits through both the platform itself and engaging GCN content.</p>",
